Scrobipalpopsis Povoln, 1967, was treated as a valid genus and brought out of synonymy by Povoln, 1993, Reichenbachia 30: 88.

Eurysacca Povoln, 1967, was established to denote a subgenus of Scrobipalpula Povoln, 1964, and was raised to generic level by Povoln, 1979, Acta Universitatis Agriculturae Facultas Agronomica (Brno) 27(2): 153. Magnifacia Povoln, 1967, was established to denote a subgenus of Scrobipalpula Povoln, 1964, and was raised to generic level by Povoln, 1987, Steenstrupia 13(1): 71.
